Lisa Vidal https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lisa_Vidal 0 Lisa Vidal (born June 13, 1965) is an American actress, best known for her roles in television series Third Watch, The Division, ER, and The Event. In 2013, Vidal began starring in the BET drama series Being Mary Jane.
